cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with the regulation of pricing policies in the context of the Internet, which is a network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also introduces game models to study the equilibria, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) or cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the monetary flow and revenues from advertisements, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
